%section
  .left
    %h2 Open Source &amp; Community Driven
    %p
      Originally STSH.ME was a way for its creators to simply upload and share screenshots. But over time the vision of the project morphed into something that would be more beneficial for the web world at large.
    %p
      That said; you can upload photos, music, videos, text files, or whatever - with a simple click+drag of a mouse, or a few nifty keystrokes.
